{"tid":1192304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住，6月9日既戰友","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T15:58:07.000Z","uid":15977,"like":2858,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"80e2fe00769f9745510cbc050b940c5196a0646c","tid":1192304,"uid":15977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"小弟係一個手停口停，又要供養兩老，又有一個幾歲小朋友既大人。<br />\n<br />\n工作係輪間制，星期日要返工，下午未能出席你地既遊行。<br />\n<br />\n但我並唔係想講我要返工，不了，喱啲廢話，而係希望大家體諒我因爲經濟問題出席唔到既原因唔係因為我唔支持你地。<br />\n<br />\n另外希望你地果日可以長時間咁支持落去，我收工會立即出黎。希望大家真係做到「不散」。做好長期抗爭既準備。<br />\n<br />\n今次可能係我地第二次兩傘運動既開始，槍口一致，對準目標，起碼要將中國剔除係逃犯條例既可移交既國家之一。<br />\n<br />\n到時見。"},{"pid":"ba8535a82f3de0b4bd5d7b7aa8cdba76dda64a47","tid":1192304,"uid":28435,"like":562,"dislike":19,"score":543,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"嚟接力啦屌"},{"pid":"4a6ffd6a927167cfd9dea99f160e2add7994f503","tid":1192304,"uid":38904,"like":254,"dislike":7,"score":247,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"加油, 體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10819148bb9a8131f69a7917ac3b6072e467a06","tid":1192304,"uid":238660,"like":322,"dislike":4,"score":318,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:03:42.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我都會去 69不散"},{"pid":"fa96a5b1eb9f93134cf8f3ab6e46fd9c6f552011","tid":1192304,"uid":74058,"like":16,"dislike":160,"score":-144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"可能要你失望"},{"pid":"61dbe8e8b800c8d65ab6fdcaa07c799de44f33b3","tid":1192304,"uid":15977,"like":118,"dislike":3,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"我會到架，大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f973ead88c4a29d860d9c65021f28e8e27403756","tid":1192304,"uid":52230,"like":106,"dislike":6,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"<span s